room_title: Escape room "Lockdown" by Digital Escape Rooms in Orlando
room_address: 3873 Avalon Park E. Blvd. Orlando, FL 32828
room_description: Establish a bulkhead onboard Station Praesidium where ABIGAIL, a hostile artificial intelligence, has ruled uncontested for hundreds of years. Together with your crewmates, assemble everything you will need to survive in a technological adventure through both real and virtual space on board the space station before ABIGAIL is able to send the space station’s… pets… to deal with you.
